description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to react to the Titans inking Ryan Tannehill to a 4-year, $118m contract (4:35). The guys discuss what the signing means for Tennessee's future and Derrick Henry's situation, as well as how the move impacts the free agent quarterback market with a focus on Tom Brady (22:30) and his impending decision.
